This will save you the frustration of having to ship a return back to us.  All decals have been rounded to the nearest inch in size.  For example, 1.499" will be measured as 1", 1.500" will be 2", so please give yourself a half inch of clearance on all edges.  For absolute specific sizes, please message us if there is any question!

What if I need another size?    Message us, we'll work with your requests the best we can!

What if I need another color?   Message us, we'll work with your requests the best we can!  We are consistently adding colors to our overall stock, and we will try to get any color that will work best for your project!

How long until I receive my item?  All items tend to be shipped within 2 business days.  United States and Canada orders can be expected within a week.  International orders can be up to 4 weeks.  

What if I need a custom wall decal?  We'll do everything we can to get what you are looking for!  Have an great idea for a product we can sell that you are looking for also?  Share it with us and receive up to 50% off regular cost as the first customer to thank you for that great idea of yours!  Just click "Request a custom order" below the pictures and we'll get back to you within 24 hours.

Any other questions?  Message us, we'll respond as soon as we can, within 24 hours the latest!

Again, thank you for viewing our items!  We'd love to hear your feedback on everything.  Have a great day!
